## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2410-160"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29> не следует вызывать до завершения загрузки документа, который его реализует.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-160"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2410-161">После обработки события <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> можно определить, завершена загрузка документа.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-161">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2410-162">В следующем примере показано, как вызвать функцию скрипта в документе из [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] приложения с помощью <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-162">The following example shows how to call a script function in a document from a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2410-163">В этом примере функция скрипта не имеет параметров.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-163">In this example, the script function has no parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2410-164">Ниже приведен [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] документ, который реализует функцию скрипта, которая будет вызываться из [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-164">The following is the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document that implements the script function that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function called!";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2410-165">Ниже показана реализация [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] для вызова функции скрипта в [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] документе.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-165">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script function in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters");  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2410-173"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> не следует вызывать до завершения загрузки документа, который его реализует.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-173"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2410-174">После обработки события <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> можно определить, завершена загрузка документа.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-174">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2410-175">Если не передать достаточное количество значений параметров в скрипт, который вызывается, то параметры, в которые не передаются значения, будут иметь неопределенное значение.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-175">If you do not pass enough parameter values to the script that you are invoking, the parameters that you do not pass values to will have the undefined value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2410-176">Если передается слишком много значений параметров, лишние значения игнорируются.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-176">If you pass too many parameter values, the excess values are ignored.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2410-177">В следующем примере показано, как вызывать функции скрипта в документе из приложения с помощью <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-177">The following example shows how to call script functions in a document from an application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2410-178">В этом примере для функций скрипта требуются параметры.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-178">In this example, the script functions require parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2410-179">Ниже приведен документ, который реализует функции скрипта, которые будут вызываться из [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-179">The following is the document that implements the script functions that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function 'called: " + message + ".";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2410-180">Ниже показана реализация [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] для вызова функций скрипта в [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] документе.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-180">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script functions in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters", this.messageTextBox.Text);  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2410-194">Вызов <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> имеет тот же результат, что и установка свойства <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-194">Calling <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> has the same effect as setting the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2410-195"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> используется из разметки разработчиками, которые хотят декларативно указывать исходный документ, который <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> переходит к моменту инициализации <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-195"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> is used from markup by developers who want to declaratively specify the initial document that <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to when <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is initialized.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2410-196">Используйте метод <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29>, чтобы перейти по URL-адресу, который может содержать символы escape.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-196">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2410-197">Используйте метод <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> для перехода к <xref:System.Uri>, который не содержит escape-символы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-197">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2410-198">В следующем примере показано, как использовать <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> для перехода к документу с помощью метода <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-198">The following example shows how to use <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> to navigate to a document by using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute. For example, 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri);  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2410-216">Используйте метод <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29>, чтобы перейти по URL-адресу, который может содержать символы escape.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-216">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2410-217">Используйте метод <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> для перехода к <xref:System.Uri>, который не содержит escape-символы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-217">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2410-218">В следующем примере показано, как перейти к документу и открыть его в новом окне браузера, указав целевой объект "about: blank".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-218">The following example shows how to navigate to a document and open it in a new browser window by specifying the "about:blank" target.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute. For example, 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri, "_blank", null, null);  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2410-229">Если параметр `stream` имеет значение `null`, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> переходит к пустому документу ("about: blank").</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-229">If the `stream` parameter is `null`, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to a blank document ("about:blank").</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2410-230">Если параметр потока имеет недопустимый формат [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)], он будет отображаться как обычный текст.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-230">If the stream parameter is not in a valid [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] format, it will be displayed as plain text.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2410-231">После навигации <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> будет `null`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-231">After navigation, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> will be `null`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2410-232">В следующем примере показано, как переходить к потоку, содержащему документ.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2410-232">The following example shows how to navigate to a stream that contains a document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateToStreamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Load HTML document as a stream  
  Uri uri = new Uri(@"pack://application:,,,/HTMLDocumentWithScript.html", UriKind.Absolute);  
  Stream source = Application.GetResourceStream(uri).Stream;  
  
  // Navigate to HTML document stream  
  this.webBrowser.NavigateToStream(source);  
}  
```

  
  
